            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> each time i change worktree (change directory) the lsp is not reinitialized with the new init_options\r\n\r\n`init_options` is sent only when the LSP server starts, right? The mechanism in `vim.lsp` for deciding when to start a new server is `reuse_client`, see `:help vim.lsp.Config`.\r\n\r\nExample: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/5f550bbb4d58bb2bfbbed4633fc69c3f0eccaf3a/lsp/ast_grep.lua#L15-L18",
